setting up angular environment:
================================

** make sure node > 8.0

sudo apt install nodejs
sudo apt install npm
npm install -g typescript

verify versions:
ng version

angular material
===================
sudo ng new retailui
cd retailui
sudo npm install --save @angular/material @angular/cdk @angular/animations @angular/http hammerjs
npm install chart.js --save
npm install ng2-charts@2.2.2 --save
npm install chartjs-plugin-datalabels --save
sudo npm i bootstrap

create component:
=================
ng g c <component_name>


create service:
=================
ng g c spark



https://bootswatch.com/flatly/

